data.description: Welcome home! This adorable property has been completely remodeled. Too many upgrades to list!!! You're immediately greeted by a grand kitchen that seamlessly flows into the expansive great room. Brand new flooring through out & baseboards! Create an inviting ambiance for your guests & friends. Impeccable kitchen boasts of ample cabinets, built-in SS appliances, new kitchen sink, new counter tops, a pantry, & a breakfast bar as an ideal spot for quick meals. The master suite showcases a brand new barn door, providing you access to a fully upgraded bathroom & a walk-in closet. The charming backyard is perfect and ready for your design with brand new rock and a wood deck to enjoy many sunsets. Make this your home sweet home!
